These are Puzzles for 3x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-1::.
There 4 different types of food: pumpkin, cabbage, apple, eggplant
4 different pets are kept: snake, hedgehog, mouse, chinchilla
The people use 4 different means of transport: airplane, taxi, boat, ship
1. the person driving the boat is on the left of the owner of the hedgehog##1
2. the person driving the ship is the owner of the snake##1
3. the person eating apple is on the far left##1
4. the person eating pumpkin is on the far right##1
5. the owner of the hedgehog is between the person driving the boat and the person eating cabbage##2
6. the person driving the taxi is the owner of the mouse##1
7. the owner of the snake is on the right of the owner of the hedgehog##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |    2    |     3     |     4      |
| Food        | apple | eggplant  | cabbage | pumpkin  |
| Pet         | chinchilla    | hedgehog  | snake       | mouse     |
| Transport   | boat     | airplane | ship       | taxi |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-2::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: puzzles, cooking, filmmaking, sudoku
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: musical, spy, crime, disaster
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: handball, skiing, badminton, golf
1. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the far left##1
2. the person who's sport is handball is on the right of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
3. the person who's sport is skiing is on the far left##1
4. the person who's sport is golf is between the person watching disaster movies and the person who's hobby is sudoku##2
5. the person watching disaster movies is the person who's sport is skiing##1
6. the person watching musical movies is on the left of the person who's sport is handball##1
7. the person watching crime movies is the person who's sport is badminton##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |    3     |      4       |
| Hobby         | cooking | puzzles    | sudoku  | filmmaking |
| Movie-Genre   | disaster  | musical  | spy   | crime    |
| Sport         | skiing | golf | handball | badminton      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-3::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, coffee, almond-milk, iced-tea
The people have 4 different hobbies: fishing, board-games, filmmaking, singing
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: punk, salsa, dubstep, techno
1. the fan of salsa is between the fan of techno and the person drinking coffee##2
2. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the left of the fan of punk##1
3. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the left of the person who's hobby is singing##1
4. the person drinking almond-milk is on the far right##1
5. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the far left##1
6. the fan of punk is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
7. the fan of dubstep is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |     3      |     4     |
| Beverage      | coffee | iced-tea         | hot-chocolate   | almond-milk    |
| Hobby         | board-games | singing | fishing | filmmaking |
| Music-Genre   | dubstep   | salsa        | techno      | punk   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-4::.
There are 4 different nationalities: nigerian, italian, colombian, pakistani
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: swimming, ice-hockey, skiing, surfing
The people use 4 different means of transport: quad-bike, jet-ski, snowmobile, roller
1. the person driving the snowmobile is on the far left##1
2. the person driving the quad-bike is between the person driving the roller and the pakistani##2
3. the colombian is on the right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
4. the person driving the quad-bike is on the right of the person who's sport is skiing##1
5. the colombian is on the right of the nigerian##1
6. the person driving the roller is between the person who's sport is swimming and the person driving the jet-ski##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2    |     3      |   4    |
| Nationality   | pakistani        | italian   | nigerian | colombian |
| Sport         | skiing | swimming | ice-hockey    | surfing |
| Transport     | snowmobile       | quad-bike     | roller       | jet-ski    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-5::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, water, soy-milk, sprite
The people have 4 different hobbies: writing, collecting, rock-climbing, skydiving
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: water-polo, skateboarding, baseball, swimming
1. the person who's sport is swimming is between the person drinking iced-tea and the person drinking water##2
2. the person who's sport is swimming is the person drinking sprite##1
3. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the far right##1
4. the person drinking water is on the left of the person drinking soy-milk##1
5. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the right of the person who's sport is baseball##1
6. the person who's sport is baseball is on the right of the person who's hobby is collecting##1
7. the person who's sport is swimming is between the person who's sport is baseball and the person who's hobby is writing##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |    2     |      3      |     4      |
| Beverage   | iced-tea | sprite      | water       | soy-milk   |
| Hobby      | writing   | collecting  | skydiving | rock-climbing     |
| Sport      | skateboarding     | swimming | baseball        | water-polo |

