.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-6::.
There 4 different types of food: spinach, pomegranate, papaya, potato
The people have 4 different hobbies: cooking, singing, video-games, sudoku
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: volleyball, golf, cycling, weightlifting
1. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the left of the person who's sport is golf##1
2. the person eating spinach is on the left of the person who's sport is cycling##1
3. the person eating spinach is on the right of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
4. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the left of the person eating pomegranate##1
5. the person who's hobby is cooking is between the person who's hobby is sudoku and the person who's sport is cycling##2
6. the person eating pomegranate is between the person eating spinach and the person eating papaya##2
7. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the right of the person who's hobby is video-games##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |     2      |   3    |     4      |
| Food    | papaya | pomegranate  | spinach | potato      |
| Hobby   | video-games  | sudoku  | cooking | singing |
| Sport   | weightlifting | volleyball | golf | cycling     |

