1. the person who's sport is sailing is the person watching sports movies##1
2. the person who's sport is soccer is the person watching action movies##1
3. the person watching documentary movies is on the far left##1
4. the person watching animation movies is on the right of the person watching documentary movies##1
5. the person eating tomato is on the left of the person who's sport is golf##1
6. the person eating cherry is between the person watching sports movies and the person watching documentary movies##2
7. the person eating raspberry is on the left of the person watching action movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |      3      |    4     |
| Food          | tomato  | cherry    | raspberry | grapes  |
| Movie-Genre   | documentary | animation       | sports        | action    |
| Sport         | biathlon | golf | sailing  | soccer |

