The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: mystery, musical, family, disaster
4 different pets are kept: goat, chinchilla, cat, ferret
1. the person watching disaster movies is on the right of the owner of the goat##1
2. the person watching musical movies is between the owner of the ferret and the person who's hobby is traveling##2
3. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the right of the owner of the cat##1
4. the owner of the cat is on the right of the owner of the goat##1
5. the person watching disaster movies is on the right of the person who's hobby is baking##1
6. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the left of the person watching family movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |    3    |      4      |
| Hobby         | baking  | traveling | drawing | magic-tricks |
| Movie-Genre   | mystery  | disaster | musical   | family         |
| Pet           | goat | cat  | chinchilla   | ferret      |

