1. the fan of classical is on the left of the fan of pop##1
2. the person who's hobby is skydiving is the person eating papaya##1
3. the fan of blues is on the left of the person eating plum##1
4. the person who's hobby is fishing is the person eating plum##1
5. the person eating papaya is on the right of the person eating kiwi##1
6. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the far right##1
7. the person who's hobby is skydiving is between the fan of classical and the person who's hobby is baking##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |   3    |      4      |
| Food          | kiwi  | papaya    | grapefruit | plum       |
| Hobby         | singing | skydiving | baking  | fishing |
| Music-Genre   | classical   | pop      | blues  | gospel     |

