3. the person eating apricot is between the person eating kiwi and the person who's hobby is photography##2
4. the person watching disaster movies is on the right of the person eating garlic##1
5. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the far right##1
6. the person watching disaster movies is on the right of the person eating garlic##1
7. the person watching crime movies is the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
8. the person watching epic movies is the person eating garlic##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2      |   3    |    4    |
