.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-11::.
There 4 different types of food: pineapple, cauliflower, papaya, broccoli
The people have 4 different hobbies: traveling, magic-tricks, gardening, drawing
4 different pets are kept: lizard, goldfish, cat, hamster
1. the person eating cauliflower is on the right of the person eating pineapple##1
2. the owner of the cat is the person eating cauliflower##1
3. the owner of the lizard is between the person who's hobby is magic-tricks and the person who's hobby is gardening##2
4. the person who's hobby is gardening is between the owner of the lizard and the person eating broccoli##2
5. the person who's hobby is gardening is the owner of the hamster##1
6. the person who's hobby is traveling is the owner of the goldfish##1
7. the person who's hobby is drawing is the owner of the lizard##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |    3     |     4      |
| Food    | broccoli  | papaya | pineapple | cauliflower     |
| Hobby   | traveling | gardening   | drawing  | magic-tricks    |
| Pet     | goldfish        | hamster       | lizard      | cat |

