3. the person drinking milk is between the person drinking soy-milk and the person who's hobby is hiking##2
4. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the far left##1
5. the person drinking milk is on the right of the owner of the lizard##1
6. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the far right##1
7. the owner of the ferret is on the right of the person drinking soy-milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |     2     |      3      |     4     |
| Beverage   | hot-chocolate | soy-milk     | milk | fanta       |
| Hobby      | board-games  | rock-climbing | drawing  | hiking |
| Pet        | snake  | lizard      | ferret        | guinea-pig      |

