3. the person drinking juice is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1
4. the person drinking lemonade is the owner of the rat##1
5. the owner of the dog is on the right of the person who's hobby is camping##1
6. the person drinking iced-tea is the person who's hobby is skydiving##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |   2    |     3      |    4    |
