1. the person watching horror movies is the person driving the helicopter##1
2. the person driving the boat is the coach##1
3. the person driving the boat is on the left of the social-worker##1
4. the person watching mystery movies is on the left of the person driving the helicopter##1
5. the person driving the train is between the person watching scientific movies and the coach##2
6. the person driving the helicopter is on the far right##1
7. the person driving the train is the bartender##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2     |      3      |    4     |
| Job           | chef | bartender | coach    | social-worker   |
| Movie-Genre   | scientific      | western   | mystery | horror |
| Transport     | tram     | train       | boat        | helicopter    |

