2. the person eating carrot is between the person drinking juice and the person who's sport is ice-hockey##2
3. the person who's sport is tennis is on the right of the person who's sport is sailing##1
4. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the far right##1
5. the person eating cauliflower is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1
6. the person eating garlic is on the right of the person eating carrot##1
7. the person drinking iced-tea is the person who's sport is biathlon##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1     |    2    |       3       |    4     |
| Beverage   | 7up    | almond-milk | juice           | iced-tea |
| Food       | cauliflower | carrot    | garlic          | potato   |
| Sport      | ice-hockey  | sailing   | tennis | biathlon  |

