1. the owner of the pony is on the far left##1
2. the person eating broccoli is on the right of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
3. the person driving the van is on the right of the owner of the pony##1
4. the person eating kiwi is on the far right##1
5. the person driving the bus is the owner of the goldfish##1
6. the owner of the guinea-pig is between the person eating cherry and the person driving the snowmobile##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2    |     3     |     4      |
| Food        | cherry | garlic | broccoli | kiwi |
| Pet         | pony       | guinea-pig     | ferret   | goldfish   |
| Transport   | subway | van | snowmobile | bus |

 